01:07:26.190 --> 01:07:30.670
By doing so, we actually glorify God. Why?

01:07:30.670 --> 01:07:33.949
Because unity identifies true worship.

01:07:33.949 --> 01:07:36.269
Micah 212 says,

01:07:36.269 --> 01:07:41.630
In unity, I shall set them like a flock in the pin.

