01:07:49.389 --> 01:07:53.070
That's why the Apostle Paul encouraged the Ephesians

01:07:53.070 --> 01:07:56.110
in chapter 4 and verse 3,

01:07:56.110 --> 01:08:01.309
earnestly endeavor to observe the oneness of the spirit.

01:08:01.309 --> 01:08:07.469
